item.title: About Me
item.description: Who Am I 10+ years old testing veteran. Be serious about entrusted things. Deem trustworthiness as supreme glory. Like knowledge sharing, sharing is an important way to consolidate what I have learned. Like delicious food. No trouble that delicious food cannot solve! Like NBA. Big love Mike Jordan, Kobe Bryant, and Stephen Curry! Love singing. People who love singing will never die! Love reading celebrities' biographies. There always something to learn from the taste of different life.
